    <article class = 'Michelangelo'>
        <h1>Michelangelo's Life</h1>
        <p>Michelangelo's most famous work was the Last Judgement which famously took him 4 years to complete, he also did other famous pieces.
            <ul> <b> His paintings included: </b>
                <li> The Entombment </li>
                <li> The Manchester Madonna</li>
                <li> Leda and the Swan </li>
                <li> The Dream of Human Life </li>
                <li> ...and many more.</li>
            </ul>
        <h3> There is more information about Michelangelo and why he was deemed the Hero of the High Renaissance on 
            <a
                id="tribute-link"
                href="https://www.nationalgallery.org.uk/artists/michelangelo"
                target="_blank"
                >National Geographic</a 
                > website.
        </h3>
        <i>As requested, using the Loren Ipsum site, I have added in text from there. "Nam tempus neque sit amet pulvinar dictum. Maecenas iaculis venenatis urna sit amet tempor. Nunc et posuere purus. Quisque et efficitur velit. Vivamus leo lorem, ornare at mi nec, rhoncus mollis est. Fusce suscipit cursus enim, id varius tortor lobortis sit amet. Nam congue, dui id dapibus facilisis, augue tortor laoreet est, sit amet cursus lacus leo a mauris. Cras vitae quam porttitor, tempus massa fringilla, iaculis justo. Aenean consequat vulputate nulla sit amet luctus. Fusce lobortis ex nec sem rhoncus gravida. Sed imperdiet finibus tellus, a lacinia enim dapibus et. Nam pulvinar auctor luctus."</i>
        </p>
